OL,3,CCountdown champion given hospital
OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,FA former Countdown champion who
OL,7,Fstabbed a rival at a fan convention in
OL,8,FBlackpool will be detained
OL,9,Findefinitely in hospital under the
OL,10,FMental Health Act, a court has been
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FJohn Cowen, 31, walked into convention
OL,14,Fvenue with a knife and, in the words
OL,15,Fof the judge "went for" fellow
OL,16,FCountdown champion Thomas Carey,
OL,17,Fstabbing him in the upper arm, a
OL,18,Fsentence hearing at Preston Crown
OL,19,FCourt was told.
