OL,3,CCountdown champion given hospital
OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,FThe incident happened on 14 September
OL,7,F2024 at a gathering of the Focal
OL,8,FCountdown Group at the Wainwright
OL,9,FSocial Club in Blackpool, where former
OL,10,Fcontestants on the Channel 4 TV quiz
OL,11,Fshow and fans meet for unofficial
OL,12,Ftournaments.
OL,14,F"You were in possession of two kitchen
OL,15,Fknives and already held one of them in
OL,16,Fyour hand ` clearly to be used as a
OL,17,Fweapon," Judge Mathieson told the
OL,18,Fcourt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
