OL,3,CCountdown champion given hospital
OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,F"This was a terrifying incident of
OL,7,Fdeliberate violence with a knife which
OL,8,Fcould have caused far more serious
OL,9,Finjury and possible lethality."
OL,11,FCowen was arrested at the scene and
OL,12,Flater charged with a wounding offence
OL,13,Fand two counts of possessing a bladed
OL,14,Farticle in a public place.
OL,16,FBut Judge Mathieson ruled earlier this
OL,17,Fyear that the defendant was unfit to
OL,18,Fstand trial because of mental illness.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
