OL,3,CCountdown champion given hospital
OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,FA fact-finding hearing took place,
OL,7,Fafter which a jury found that Cowen,
OL,8,Ffrom Morecambe, had committed the act
OL,9,Fof wounding as charged.
OL,11,FJudge Mathieson said Cowen never
OL,12,Foffered an explanation for his
OL,13,Factions, although the court previously
OL,14,Fheard he had expressed discontent over
OL,15,Fthe use of an app by some of those at
OL,16,Fthe conventions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
