OL,3,CCountdown champion given hospital
OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,F"The one matter that was tentatively
OL,7,Fput to Mr Carey was that there had
OL,8,Fbeen some ongoing disagreement between
OL,9,Fyou, Mr Cowen, and others on the use
OL,10,Fof an app to play or help with playing
OL,11,FCountdown," Judge Mathieson told the
OL,12,Fhearing on Wednesday.
OL,14,F"Mr Carey was at a complete loss as to
OL,15,Fwhy he had been singled out for this
OL,16,Fattack."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
