OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,FThe judge ordered that Cowen, who is
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with schizophrenia, be
OL,8,Fdetained in hospital for an
OL,9,F"indefinite duration" under the Mental
OL,10,FHealth Act.
OL,12,FCowen, who appeared via videolink from
OL,13,Fthe Guild Lodge psychiatric hospital
OL,14,Fin Preston, where he is undergoing
OL,15,Fmedical treatment, did not react to
OL,16,Fthe decision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
