OL,3,CCountdown champion given hospital
OL,4,Corder after stabbing fellow contestant
OL,6,F"Your attitude to that treatment
OL,7,Fremains hostile and so any potential
OL,8,Ftreatment and monitoring in the
OL,9,Fcommunity would not be effective as
OL,10,Fyou would not engage," Judge Mathieson
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"I am satisfied that you, Mr Cowen,
OL,14,Fare suffering from a mental disorder
OL,15,Fof such a nature that it is
OL,16,Fappropriate for you to be detained in
OL,17,Fhospital for medical treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
