OL,6,FCowen will also be subject to a
OL,7,Frestriction order, meaning his
OL,8,Fdischarge from hospital would require
OL,9,Fthe consent of the Secretary of State
OL,10,Ffor Justice.
OL,12,FCowen appeared on Countdown in 2017,
OL,13,Fwhen he scored the third highest total
OL,14,Fof the series in which he was a
OL,15,Fcontestant, including spotting the
OL,16,Fnine-letter word spreading.
OL,18,FHe competed in a further 11 episodes,
OL,19,Fwinning eight consecutive contests,
OL,20,Fbefore he was finally defeated.
